{"tid":701503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[A組 - 2018世界杯] 23:00 14/6 俄羅斯 對 沙地阿拉伯","createTime":"2018-06-14T07:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T15:15:01.000Z","uid":78873,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"150e81ab252900fc550427f25f76a22ed78a244a","tid":701503,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/144204_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F144204_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG&h=071e93c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/144418_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F144418_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG&h=35ad64fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>焦點球員：</ins></strong></span><br />\n<strong>Artem Dzuyba  迪蘇巴 (Russia)</strong><br />\n位置：正前鋒<br />\n效力球會：辛尼特 (俄超)<br />\n辛尼特及俄羅斯國家隊前線數糊人物，身高達1米96。沙地可謂今屆世界杯其中一隊防守最差球隊，身體對抗性及身高都是零的沙地，勢必放大迪蘇巴的身高優勢。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.livetvcdn.net/img/images/70/42970_c1a00de3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.livetvcdn.net%2Fimg%2Fimages%2F70%2F42970_c1a00de3.jpg&h=79f62128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Salem Al-Dawsari 沙林 艾杜沙里 (Saudi Arabia)</strong><br />\n位置：翼鋒<br />\n效力球會： 維拉利爾 (西甲)<br />\n於2017年曾恊助希拉爾殺入亞冠杯決賽，雖然最終不敵浦和紅鑽，其出色的盤帶技術和高速，不斷為對手帶來極大壓力。2018年更外借至維拉利爾發展。俄羅斯如希望在首戰取得重要3分，或許取決於能否應付艾杜沙里的進襲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/78/7e/arabia-saudita-camiseta-alternativa-saudi-arabia-away-kit-2018_h430sudj261a1072easf7yg1g.jpg?t=1574905058\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F78%2F7e%2Farabia-saudita-camiseta-alternativa-saudi-arabia-away-kit-2018_h430sudj261a1072easf7yg1g.jpg%3Ft%3D1574905058&h=485493e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>GROUP A</ins><br />\n<br />\n1.Russia<br />\n2.Saudi Arabia<br />\n3.Egypt<br />\n4.Uruguay</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0f19de074cbca242cd9f0d0248ed71fd5bd9f0d2","tid":701503,"uid":136625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:55:42.000Z","msg":"All in俄羅斯 上車機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c511e6e298f4ae1dbafc987bbb6b0685b8f1d3c1","tid":701503,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f19de074cbca242cd9f0d0248ed71fd5bd9f0d2","tid":701503,"uid":136625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:55:42.000Z","msg":"All in俄羅斯 上車機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"1.0都豬半"},{"pid":"61dca9da850d95da8f67772608bed2162055f1d5","tid":701503,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0f19de074cbca242cd9f0d0248ed71fd5bd9f0d2","tid":701503,"uid":136625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:55:42.000Z","msg":"All in俄羅斯 上車機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"冷推沙特客勝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成功致富記得比番個正皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2b37d0b50a2d9c007be97f166732923d4a2d4d","tid":701503,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"俄佬機會應該大d，但係隔離10倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee5130b65474252e2be7f26cc81e1192719293e","tid":701503,"uid":65021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"買左湯地下盤"},{"pid":