eta-alternativa-saudi-arabia-away-kit-2018_h430sudj261a1072easf7yg1g.jpg?t=1574905058\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F78%2F7e%2Farabia-saudita-camiseta-alternativa-saudi-arabia-away-kit-2018_h430sudj261a1072easf7yg1g.jpg%3Ft%3D1574905058&h=485493e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>GROUP A</ins><br />\n<br />\n1.Russia<br />\n2.Saudi Arabia<br />\n3.Egypt<br />\n4.Uruguay</strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:45:48.000Z","msg":"焦點球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ZUYBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37349acd02154c02317651f0b33ce23e0d1e7426","tid":701503,"uid":12568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"今晚多唔多人買沙地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8b4083b7b986d6de3d5ae645d214dcb57232f8","tid":701503,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37349acd02154c02317651f0b33ce23e0d1e7426","tid":701503,"uid":12568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"今晚多唔多人買沙地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"買咗100蚊沙地客勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俄佬入球能力好低，當然對沙地，加上主場因勢，打道氣應該都仲有啲野睇，加上普京個面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但沙地啲人有啲速度同技術，俄佬輕敵係真係隨時比佢地冼到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38d22f59998d9d1ab11f75ee2c25c4e1ffffbaf","tid":701503,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dba1e29cff64fa8ca9bac51b72097177d9b2a93","tid":701503,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"150e81ab252900fc550427f25f76a22ed78a244a","tid":701503,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/144204_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F144204_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.JPG&h=071e93c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/144418_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F144418_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.JPG&h=35ad64fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>焦點球員：</ins></strong></span><br />\n<strong>Artem Dzuyba  迪蘇巴 (Russia)</strong><br />\n位置：正前鋒<br />\n效力球會：辛尼特 (俄超)<br />\n辛尼特及俄羅斯國家隊前線數糊人物，身高達1米96。沙地可謂今屆世界杯其中一隊防守最差球隊，身體對抗性及身高都是零的沙地，勢必放大迪蘇巴的身高優勢。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.livetvcdn.net/img/images/70/42970_c1a00de3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.livetvcdn.net%2Fimg%2Fimages%2F70%2F42970_c1a00de3.jpg&h=79f62128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Salem Al-Dawsari 沙林 艾杜沙里 (Saudi Arabia)</strong><br />\n位置：翼鋒<br />\n效力球會： 維拉利爾 (西甲)<br />\n於2017年曾恊助希拉爾殺入亞冠杯決賽，雖然最終不敵浦和紅鑽，其出色的盤帶技術和高速，不斷為對手帶來極大壓力。2018年更外借至維拉利爾發展。俄羅斯如希望在首戰取得重要3分，或許取決於能否應付艾杜沙里的進襲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/78/7e/arabia-saudita-camiseta-alternativa-saudi-arabia-away-kit-2018_h430sudj261a1072easf7yg1g.jpg?t=1574905058\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F78%2F7e%2Farabia-saudita-camiseta-alternativa-saudi-arabia-away-kit-2018_h430sudj261a1072easf7yg1g.jpg%3Ft%3D1574905058&h=485493e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><ins>GROUP A</ins><br />\n<br />\n1.Russia<br />\n2.Saudi Arabia<br />\n3.Egypt<br />\n4.Uruguay</strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:45:48.000Z","msg":"焦點球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ZUYBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:08:54.000Z","msg":"閣下睇邊個俄佬球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14f8311e5f32b0a78201309b9b77a95f85d05d9","tid":701503,"uid":141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"Let&rsquo;s go Smolov!"},{"pid":"ca530848713ae43bc1e3ae13a818901f5e795b81","tid":701503,"uid":176304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"ALL IN 左沙特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中左又係一個日本旅行"},{"pid":"cfa4d8dd249cd1386a432ae8097f9f1419c7eba8","tid":701503,"uid":21708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:10:42.000Z","msg":"沙地穩袋半格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1cf7fb40c15acbb355d17cc7842593cd952b5f","tid":701503,"uid":78873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca530848713ae43bc1e3ae13a818901f5e795b81","tid":701503,"uid":176304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"ALL IN 左沙特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中左又係一個日本旅行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"All in都係去日本咋,係都去俄羅斯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57db74da24bae859b2fdefcbe9808fbb320